          "slidetitle": "Key Points to Remember",
          "subtitle": "Core lessons for responsible AI use",
          "slidecontent": "• Always verify AI-generated edits, VFX outputs, and automated decisions before they reach the final cut\n• Bias and errors can enter workflows silently\n• Keep a human editor in the loop at every critical stage of post-production\n• Understand the tools you rely on, even at a basic level, so you can spot when something has gone wrong\n• Document where and how AI is used across your production pipeline\n• As a next step, audit one current workflow and identify where AI decisions could benefit from closer human review"
